Summary: Not the first time I have seen a UFO by my house. This one was right out back of our house.
trends: There have been 16 other sightings in Frederick
There were no other sightings in Frederick on or around October 14th 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsWent out to smoke a cigarette with my boyfriend I'm my backyard and look southwest to see a saucer shaped object in our view. The lights were rotating around the ship with blue, white, and red lights. It clearly was not a plane or helicopter because it did not make any noise and it was not moving - just hovering. We stayed out to watch it until it slowly backed away out of our reach. Very strange
